{"tid":2353136,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名華裔商人將被澳洲驅逐出境","createTime":"2021-01-04T13:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T04:00:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd92f6e30ffc56d1276c1500ca44e8a4f1d97e7","tid":2353136,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"一名華裔商人將被澳洲驅逐出境<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418985&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=2fbe21fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418985&h=8c27a537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418985</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】澳洲傳媒報道，當地一名華裔商人，被認為對國家有安全風險，將會被驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司報道，墨爾本華裔商人、52歲的劉煇峰，是現時澳洲執政聯盟中，自由黨的捐款人之一，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">曾經加入解放軍當兵。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報道指，劉煇峰與在香港出生，其後移居到澳洲的自由黨聯邦國會議員廖嬋娥，以及澳洲助理財長蘇卡爾相熟，又指劉煇峰移居澳洲後，2016年成立緊急互援協會，專門在涉及警方或法律事件中，為講中文的人充當中間人。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司又聲稱獲得機密文件，該協會獲中國駐墨爾本領事館承諾提供資金，並同意匯報中國公民的刑事案件、遇到的緊急情況或事故。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，劉煇峰申請永久居留時，被澳洲安全情報組織評估為有國家安全風險，正面臨被驅逐出境，劉煇峰本人就強調沒犯法，相信法庭會還他公道。"},{"pid":"aadb29b53364f15627574a60b5767fcfed19ae7a","tid":2353136,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"廖嬋娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abca0a06466aea78169bc9623341fdb80e435645","tid":2353136,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"CLS入籍澳洲。如果澳洲出事都照搵中國駐澳洲大使館求助，咁即係視澳洲為殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bCtiKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bCtiKT.jpg&h=0ac18a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"590820d52066d63c6b0ae847ca568b3fbce94eaa","tid":2353136,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"好可惜要打官司 沒得直接趕走"},{"pid":"762fbad7f8e951e4cf9565b1b0a341c626f0b270","tid":2353136,"uid":8918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"之前仲有個黃向墨"},{"pid":"c4b4f1847323763f6086deb664f3eba71b47e734","tid":2353136,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab708f303d95c08fe543b9359c9927cdf2be532","tid":2353136,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac60222521d04ac4fdd1f642c2dff6651dca1c81","tid":2353136,"uid":363016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aadb29b53364f15627574a60b5767fcfed19ae7a","tid":2353136,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"廖嬋娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"陳玉娥 鄭月娥<br />\n娥字輩冇一個好人"},{"pid":"dd155621ab79478feb392765f3ea571644e38c2b","tid":2353136,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abca0a06466aea78169bc9623341fdb80e435645","tid":2353136,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"CLS入籍澳洲。如果澳洲出事都照搵中國駐澳洲大使館求助，咁即係視澳洲為殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bCtiKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bCtiKT.jpg&h=0ac18a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T02:48:32.000Z","msg"